  <brief_title>A Study of Vinflunine in Patients With Gastric Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Single-Arm, Phase II Study of Single-Agent Vinflunine in the Second-line Treatment of Patients With Gastric Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
