  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to learn if vinflunine can shrink or slow the growth of cancer
      in patients with advanced or metastatic stomach cancer who have progressed on a prior
      treatment with a fluoropyrimidine or taxane-containing chemotherapy regimen. The safety of
      this treatment will also be studied.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
